        <updateDate>2020-02-21T18:20:54Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Retain Innovation and Manufacturing Excellence (RIME) Act of 2019</b></p> <p>This bill directs the Department of Commerce to establish a pilot grant program to help eligible manufacturers retain retiring employees for up to 90 days&nbsp;for the purpose of&nbsp;transferring&nbsp;job-specific skills and training to other employees.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
